00:49:57,440 --> 00:50:01,360
I hired you, but you're sleeping in
working hours?! I'm docking your pay!

549
00:50:01,440 --> 00:50:05,680
You can punch me if you want, just don't touch
my salary! I don't even have enough to get by.

550
00:50:05,880 --> 00:50:07,600
It's okay to be scared, Sailom.

551
00:50:07,800 --> 00:50:09,520
There's nothing wrong with that.

552
00:50:09,600 --> 00:50:14,160
Fear just makes you more careful
about starting a relationship.

